categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the New Jedi Order

nodes.text: A member of the New Jedi Order, this Human fought in a battle and was badly injured. After the battle ended, the Jedi was found by Chief Healer Cilghal who healed him.
This Jedi was created for the Wizards of the Coast Star Wars Roleplaying Game. Unnamed, he was placed on a card displaying Cilghal's healing abilities.
